---
import perfil from "../assets/perfil.jpg"
---
<div class="relative w-full h-full bg-gray-900 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">


    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-15">
        <div class="w-full h-full relative">
            <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/af/Tux.png" class="w-36 absolute top-10 left-10" />
            <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/3f/Fedora_logo.svg" class="w-24 absolute top-1/4 right-20" />
            <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/66/Openlogo-debianV2.svg" class="w-24 absolute bottom-10 left-1/3" />
            <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/3e/Manjaro-logo.svg" class="w-28 absolute bottom-1/3 left-10" />
            <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/1/13/Arch_Linux_%22Crystal%22_icon.svg" class="w-28 absolute bottom-10 right-10" />
            <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/1/13/Arch_Linux_%22Crystal%22_icon.svg" class="w-28 absolute bottom-10 right-1/3" />
            <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/2/2b/Kali-dragon-icon.svg" class="w-40 absolute top-16 right-1/3" />
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20 flex items-center justify-center gap-10">
        <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/af/Tux.png" class="w-40" alt="Linux" />
        <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/3f/Fedora_logo.svg" class="w-40" alt="Fedora" />
        <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/66/Openlogo-debianV2.svg" class="w-40" alt="Debian" />
    </div>


    <div class="relative bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md p-10 rounded-2xl shadow-lg text-center w-3/4 max-w-3xl my-36">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Proyecto de sistemas operativos</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-200 mb-8">Integrantes del grupo 4</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 justify-center">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="size-60 mx-auto rounded-full border-4 border-white overflow-hidden bg-gray-700">
                <img src={perfil.src} alt="Integrante" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
            </div>
            <p class="text-white mt-1 text-lg">Joan Sebastian Oviedo Mosquera</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="size-60 mx-auto rounded-full border-4 border-white overflow-hidden bg-gray-700">
                <img src={perfil.src} alt="Integrante" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
            </div>
            <p class="text-white mt-1 text-lg">Anghelo Garcia Cordoba</p>
        </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-10 bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-md p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg text-left text-gray-200">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Proyecto final de semestre de la materia sistemas operativos de la Universidad del Valle donde veremos temas como la distribucion de linux fedora en entorno grafico, debian en entorno consola, bash, manejo de procesos, docker y kubernetes</h2>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Objetivos</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                <li>Aprender a usar distribucion de linux fedora en entorno grafico</li>
                <li>Aprender a usar distribucion de linux debian en entorno consola</li>
                <li>Aprender sintaxis de bash, procesos en linux, hilos en java</li>
                <li>Aprender el uso de Docker</li>
                <li>Aprender el uso de kuberntes</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>